## ============================================================
## FRONTEND ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (IntellyWeave)
## ============================================================
## Copy this file to .env.local and configure your values

## ============================================================
## MAPBOX CONFIGURATION (IntellyWeave-specific, not in upstream Elysia)
## ============================================================
## Required for geospatial entity visualization on maps
## Get your free token at: https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_ACCESS_TOKEN=pk.your-mapbox-token-here



NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_STYLE_URL=mapbox://styles/yourusernamehere/cmhuxxxxxxxxxxxj

## API Configuration
## Set to "true" when building static export (no backend)
## Leave unset or "false" for development with backend
NEXT_PUBLIC_IS_STATIC=false

## Backend URL (only used when NEXT_PUBLIC_IS_STATIC !== "true")
## Defaults to http://localhost:8000 in development
# NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8000

## Node Environment
NODE_ENV=development
